					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"郁子", "Ikuko"},
					"“Oh, great idea! We take advantage of the confusion and hame our way into Darling’s heart!♪”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“啊，真是个好主意！搞不好还能趁乱和亲爱的做那种行为和这种勾当～♪”",
